name: Real Doll
description:
This merge use Figma Anime Figures LORA and bunch of other checkpoints to create a doll looking anime. Works best for close up picture. In the examples I Use hires. fix, upscale latent, denoising 0.5, hires steps 20, upscale by 2 . Clip skip 2

I use night sky yozora VAE in the examples https://civitai.com/api/download/models/14459?type=VAE

if you like the models, you can support me on https://ko-fi.com/promptsharingsamaritan
